OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780330269
OL,3,CEngland set off from Birmingham
OL,4,CAirport for World Cup
OL,6,FManager Thomas Tuchel has vowed to add
OL,7,Fa second star to the shirt this
OL,8,Fsummer, but this will be one of the
OL,9,Ftoughest assignments yet, given the
OL,10,Fconditions and logistics involved in a
OL,11,Ftournament spanning three countries
OL,12,Fand four time zones.
OL,14,FFive days of acclimatisation to the
OL,15,Fstifling heat ` temperatures at their
OL,16,FPalm Beach training camp are expected
OL,17,Fto be north of 30C ` will be followed
OL,18,Fby a pre-tournament friendly against
OL,19,FNew Zealand in Tampa Bay on Saturday,
OL,20,FJune 6th.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
