OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780330269
OL,3,CEngland set off from Birmingham
OL,4,CAirport for World Cup
OL,6,FTuchel's men then head to Orlando for
OL,7,Fa final warm-up game with Costa Rica
OL,8,Fon Wednesday, June 10th, before a few
OL,9,Fdays of rest ahead of moving to their
OL,10,Ftournament base in Kansas City.
OL,12,FEngland's Group L opener is against
OL,13,FCroatia in Dallas on Wednesday, June
OL,14,F17th.
OL,16,FThomas Tuchel was hired as Sir Gareth
OL,17,FSouthgate's successor in November 2024
OL,18,Fwith the brief of winning this
OL,19,Ftournament.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
