OL,3,CEngland set off from Birmingham
OL,4,CAirport for World Cup
OL,6,FThe German, who was told by his agent
OL,7,Fhe could never manage England due to
OL,8,Fhis nationality, outlined his plans
OL,9,Fwhen he first met his players in March
OL,10,F2025.
OL,12,FIn a team meeting, shown during the
OL,13,Ffirst episode of a Football
OL,14,FAssociation documentary, Tuchel showed
OL,15,Fhis players a chart titled Mount
OL,16,FEverest Summit and explained it with a
OL,17,Frousing speech, saying: "I want to
OL,18,Farrive here at the top, with the
OL,19,Ftoughest group in the world.
OL,26,@yD@YOU
