OL,3,CEngland set off from Birmingham
OL,4,CAirport for World Cup
OL,6,F"When we arrive on the plane and land,
OL,7,Fwe will already know that this will be
OL,8,Fa great camp and this will be a team
OL,9,Fno one wants to play against.
OL,11,F"And they will feel it in the mixed
OL,12,Fzone, they will feel it in the tunnel,
OL,13,Fthey will smell it."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
